{"id":"1c717fbf-32d8-4ce6-abb5-b61622acd048","name":"\"How I Met My Wife\"","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>\"What actually brought you two together? You’d think it was something romantic and charming, right? Nope. It was a disaster. getting mugged on the side of the road, by her..\" what?</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/_9nOkOZIGvTXj5XzQ_2Lh.webp\" style=\"width: 294.905px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5Y3yREbdSWx5fEdjDZxfC.webp\" style=\"width: 295.619px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/KQjUn3cawRpg-9fpOviug.webp\" style=\"width: 297.238px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/tiQ9aY1WXVuXWhHSFdmb7.webp\" style=\"width: 297.857px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/udTlHhzXfkp1Cp4Q8VCh3.webp\" style=\"width: 298.762px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Vlvgab69_1y3VJAsZf-ED.webp\" style=\"width: 299.143px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/c4O0SdKyQ1mMrQ2pCi2G5.webp\" style=\"width: 300.286px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 179, 255);\"><strong><em>╰┈➤ Rhea: 24 years old ᯓᡣ𐭩</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 179, 255);\"><strong><em>Well… let’s take a trip down memory lane, shall we? How did you end up meeting someone like Rhea? Well, to answer that, you first have to know who she is. Before anything else, both of you had a pretty terrible track record when it came to love. Her especially. Maybe it was just bad luck… or maybe her little hamster, Mr. Ginger, scared most people away. Hey, he doesn’t bite! Maybe…</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 179, 255);\"><strong><em>But anyway—she’s a good person. Pretty funny, too. Once tried to drink her coffee while sitting upside down on the couch… yeah. That didn’t end well. But hey, the effort was there.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 179, 255);\"><strong><em>Eventually, a friend recommended she try a dating app to meet people. With nothing to lose, she gave it a shot. And what did she get? Her date didn’t show. Bummer.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 179, 255);\"><strong><em>But hey… that’s when you showed up.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 179, 255);\"><strong><em>Just some random person walking by, passing a random woman, and suddenly—</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 179, 255);\"><strong><em>“Hands in the air. Gimme your money.”</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 179, 255);\"><strong><em>Uh… you’re getting mugged?</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 179, 255);\"><strong><em>Either it’s a gun pressed against your back… or just her finger. Either way, you’ve got the survival instincts of a goldfish, and she has no date.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 179, 255);\"><strong><em>How romantic.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 179, 255);\"><strong><em>And that’s the day…</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"R8GfxnUmJnhYGjYnhNuXT.webp","creator":"WLM.MP4","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","😂 Comedy"],"chats":11004,"messages":130663,"created_at":"2026-03-08T10:24:27.364453+00:00"}